==== Quick guide ====

The email subject, html, and plain text can be parameterized using variables like $lastname$. The contents of these variables can be provided via the ''parameters'' using [[Help:AdvancedWidgetConfiguration| dynamic operators]]:

<div class="sourceDiv">
subject = Message for $lastname$<br/>

parameters:<br/>
name = lastname<br/>
value = ''$''this.rdfs:label<i>$</i>
</div>

The parameter value is dynamically read from the task context (also see [[Help:Tasks]]). If this value is resolved to be "Smith", then the email subject will be "Message for Smith".

Also note that sending email must be configured here: [[Setup:Email]].